    "For example, commercial data need not be so-but they can be if they reveal sensitive preferences-e.g., buying a \"Make America Great Again\" cap.",
    "Not all behavioral predictions are equal in terms of their consequences and the privacy risks they carry for the individual.",
    "Predicting that a specific individual is likely to purchase a house, given their age and socio-economic characteristics, is not the same as predicting that a person is likely to commit a crime, given past misdemeanors.",
    "Similarly, a commercial prediction need not carry the same privacy risk as a political prediction.",
    "5 Artificially intelligent polls are fueled by Big Data."
